1. Abstraction 🔥
👉 Abstraction ka matlab hota hai sirf essential details show karna aur unnecessary details hide karna.

Example:
java
Copy
Edit
abstract class Bank {
    abstract void interestRate(); // Abstract Method
}

class SBI extends Bank {
    void interestRate() {
        System.out.println("SBI Interest Rate is 7%");
    }
}

class HDFC extends Bank {
    void interestRate() {
        System.out.println("HDFC Interest Rate is 8%");
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Bank bank = new SBI(); // Abstraction
        bank.interestRate();
    }
}
🎯 Output:
csharp
Copy
Edit
SBI Interest Rate is 7%
